snippet.title: [Amstrad CPC] Rollaround - Longplay
snippet.description:
Rollaround
© Mastertronic (1988)

Collect the squares while avoiding the aliens and keep your balance without going over the edge or falling down any of the nasty holes before your time runs out to reach the bonus and complete the level.

*The game has 20 levels there is no end, after the 19th level we start again at level 0.
